c=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同個細路仔玩下玩具咁樣<br />\n就收一大堆錢 根本就完全冇專業可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ac37430f5090efdcd9b1ec8d577831415367ee","tid":479630,"uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNursing、Accounting、Hotel Management<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀左兩年accounting後尾覺得無用tran左科轉左major</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. IT Support<br />\n<br />\n2. Web Programmer (For most business website, excluding complex website like Google)<br />\n<br />\n3. Sales and Marketing Personnel (但medical sales和保健產品的sales就應有返科學相關學位) （可惜香港係掉返轉，醫療保健產品sales冇學位，金融保險sales就有學位，sosad）<br />\n<br />\n4. Primary School Teacher<br />\n<br />\n5. Application Programmer (For most customerized business applications, excluding for complex software development)"},{"pid":"67f3e3b6d47e30f831de65851283207c8b279f6a","tid":479630,"uid":106798,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:28:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNursing、Accounting、Hotel Management<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀左兩年accounting後尾覺得無用tran左科轉左major</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nnursing 好專囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無話nursing唔專 degree course包左好多唔關major嘅科目 好聽啲叫做思維訓練 但係nursing accounting有無必要讀呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大學訓練唔係職業訓練喎"},{"pid":"1f5a1f1ab014c461af878020b2535c97d3644c81","tid":479630,"uid":106798,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>職業治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同個細路仔玩下玩具咁樣<br />\n就收一大堆錢 根本就完全冇專業可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學位化同專業無咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過幾認同職業治療/物理治療唔應該學位化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766ec58f8ef5050a78084606fc1e5830ac725096","tid":479630,"uid":106798,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNursing、Accounting、Hotel Management<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀左兩年accounting後尾覺得無用tran左科轉左major</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. IT Support<br />\n<br />\n2. Web Programmer (For most business website, excluding complex website like Google)<br />\n<br />\n3. Sales and Marketing Personnel (但medical sales和保健產品的sales就應有返科學相關學位) （可惜香港係掉返轉，醫療保健產品sales冇學位，金融保險sales就有學位，sosad）<br />\n<br />\n4. Primary School Teacher<br />\n<br />\n5. Application Programmer (For most customerized business applications, excluding for complex software development)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 個啲好多都係讀biomedical engineering出身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過講真sales係無得讀 屌 執生都有得讀架話 個世界唔會有咁撚多蠢人"},{"pid":"04565d9be1b6473b60e8bd72a4b615e313e95630","tid":479630,"uid":64131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"老人學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中大poly東大都有  <br />\n根本只係升sw 同nursing master 跳板"},{"pid":"10789739d644e09fb971c52d0fb9915d860e346f","tid":479630,"uid":143269,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bloc