e><br />\n<br />\n咁即係 職業導向科目/專科 唔應該學位化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmbbs都唔洗讀 唔關major既course 喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我比較支持美式教育制度<br />\n想讀medic唔係問題，至少你要有個science degree先可以apply medical school<br />\n讀law一樣，你想讀law架話 至少要有個BA做first degree<br />\nA-level年代仲好少少 起碼有兩年比你學返d基礎野先揀degree DSE真係戇鳩鳩 Foundation knowledge都未讀完就叫你揀mbbs/llb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2dc4fa092ede8ca761c23ac685c1f25a621068","tid":479630,"uid":106798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNursing、Accounting、Hotel Management<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀左兩年accounting後尾覺得無用tran左科轉左major</blockquote><br />\nTran左去邊</blockquote><br />\nSocial Science 諗住grad左再讀個second degree"},{"pid":"4192ce692a5781a2cd114e7a12c8eb62febc2282","tid":479630,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"動物傳心師"},{"pid":"f09f6e760256bc03b615498e9565e362945727f9","tid":479630,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"匪犬，自稱專業，又要做雞又要......"},{"pid":"f32f9175ce27acd92b3fef404a2898dd3c80d63c","tid":479630,"uid":132594,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T14:50:19.000Z","msg":"For what does a university exist ?  What is the true nature of a university ?"},{"pid":"6177a5209af695d06bfd3a00557475d7f22fc4f7","tid":479630,"uid":149864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2476616cdb64206f13f31fe862235181cab1777e","tid":479630,"uid":16650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T19:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>職業治療<