normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d1af567f1414cc7ec7438783ad08dd18f10b9a","tid":479630,"uid":146621,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNursing、Accounting、Hotel Management<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀左兩年accounting後尾覺得無用tran左科轉左major</blockquote><br />\n每一科都有自己嘅價值<br />\n唔係學位化嘅問題<br />\n係學額嘅問題<br />\n最好行返以前嘅精英制<br />\n三大以外嘅 U downgrade 返變大專，讀副學士 high dip嗰 d <br />\ni 大就讀 dip<br />\n<br />\n利申：非三大畢業"},{"pid":"1731c133b5307772596039097c696c32264b4e06","tid":479630,"uid":149978,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:32:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNursing、Accounting、Hotel Management<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀左兩年accounting後尾覺得無用tran左科轉左major</blockquote><br />\n每一科都有自己嘅價值<br />\n唔係學位化嘅問題<br />\n係學額嘅問題<br />\n最好行返以前嘅精英制<br />\n三大以外嘅 U downgrade 返變大專，讀副學士 high dip嗰 d <br />\ni 大就讀 dip<br />\n<br />\n利申：非三大畢業</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十間大學其實唔算多<br />\n<br />\n學位泛濫主要係 top up degree  + 各大持續進修學院 + 遙距 + 網上大學 + 公開大學"},{"pid":"448b3a83dc539244be0209f8687d20fcc27b15a0","tid":479630,"uid":129573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nNursing、Accounting、Hotel Management<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀左兩年accoun